OL,3,CMum tells dangerous drivers, 'my 11-
OL,4,Cyear-old son was killed by an insecure
OL,5,Cload'
OL,7,FA bereaved mother has been speaking to
OL,8,Fdrivers stopped by police for carrying
OL,9,Fan insecure load, telling them that is
OL,10,Fhow her son died.
OL,12,FIn December 2022, Maria Dennis lost
OL,13,Fher son Harry, who was 11, when an
OL,14,Funsecured scaffold board went through
OL,15,Fthe windscreen of the car he was
OL,16,Ftravelling in.
OL,18,FThe driver is serving a four-year
OL,19,Fprison sentence.
