OL,3,CMum tells dangerous drivers, 'my 11-
OL,4,Cyear-old son was killed by an insecure
OL,5,Cload'
OL,7,FMaria joined Sussex Police officers as
OL,8,Fthey carried out road safety checks,
OL,9,Fpleading with people to secure their
OL,10,Floads properly before they get behind
OL,11,Fthe wheel.
OL,13,FShe says she hopes sharing her
OL,14,Fexperiences with drivers will make
OL,15,Fthem sit up and take notice
OL,17,FMaria Dennis said: "My goal is today
OL,18,Fto tell them what could happen, what
OL,19,Fhas happened to us and to Harry.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
