OL,3,CMum tells dangerous drivers, 'my 11-
OL,4,Cyear-old son was killed by an insecure
OL,5,Cload'
OL,7,F"I know life's busy, but it just takes
OL,8,Fan extra five minutes of extra
OL,9,Fchecking and checking that everything
OL,10,Fis secure and that it's not going to
OL,11,Fmove.
OL,13,F"A few of the drivers I've spoken to,
OL,14,Fthey've got kids themselves, they've
OL,15,Fgot lads that are 13 - the same age
OL,16,FHarry would have been now, and it does
OL,17,Fhit home. A couple of them have got
OL,18,Fquite choked up."
