OL,3,CMum tells dangerous drivers, 'my 11-
OL,4,Cyear-old son was killed by an insecure
OL,5,Cload'
OL,7,FThe action today (6 September) saw
OL,8,Fpolice have been stopping drivers to
OL,9,Fcheck if their loads are secure and to
OL,10,Fcheck the weight of their vehicles.
OL,12,FIf drivers were found to have an
OL,13,Finsecure load, they were not able to
OL,14,Fcarry on their journeys until it was
OL,15,Fsecured.
OL,17,FSome of those who failed the road
OL,18,Fsafety check were given words of
OL,19,Fadvice, others were given a #100 fine.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
