OL,3,CMum tells dangerous drivers, 'my 11-
OL,4,Cyear-old son was killed by an insecure
OL,5,Cload'
OL,7,FCommercial Vehicle Unit for Sussex
OL,8,FPolice, PC Barry Freeman said: "When
OL,9,Fyou get up in the morning you don't
OL,10,Fget up and say today I'm going to go
OL,11,Fout and kill someone - it's a set of
OL,12,Fcircumstances.
OL,14,F"It comes down to training, but what I
OL,15,Fwould say to any driver is, before
OL,16,Fthey drive off, make sure your load is
OL,17,Fsecure. Ask yourself is it safe, is it
OL,18,Fsecure and is it legal?
